text: Head of the River may refer to more than one type of rowing competition: * Bumps race ** Eights Week, Oxford University (May) ** Lent Bumps, Cambridge University (February–March) ** May Bumps, Cambridge University (June) ** Torpids, Oxford University (March) * Head race * Head of the River Amstel (the Netherlands) * Head of the River (Australia) * Head of the River (New South Wales) * Head of the River (Victoria) * Head of the River (Western Australia) * Head of the River Race, London * Women's Eights Head of the River Race, London ==See also== * Riverhead (disambiguation)
title: Head of the River
